title: Trump National Security Advisor under fire for alleged contact with Russia | On Air
text:
Trump National Security Advisor under fire for alleged contact with Russia Feb. 13, 2017 - 6:54 - Former U.S. Ambassador to the U.N. John Bolton on the controversy over allegations National Security Advisor Mike Flynn lied about being in contact with the Russians before President Trump took office.
